gw.api.web.payment

Class ProRataReversedPaymentAmountRedistributionStrategy

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.web.payment.DistributionStrategy
      • gw.api.web.payment.ProRataDistributionStrategy
        • gw.api.web.payment.ProRataRedistributionStrategy
          • gw.api.web.payment.ProRataReversedPaymentAmountRedistributionStrategy

  • public class ProRataReversedPaymentAmountRedistributionStrategy
extends ProRataRedistributionStrategy
    Class to determine the priority algorithm to redistribute reversed payment amount towards a list of dist items. The items presumably already have amounts distributed on them, and these amounts will remain, we will only distribute the excess funds on top of these distributions, which is why this extends ProRataRedistributionStrategy. Since we would also only distribute to same sign items as the allocation amount, isEnoughMoneyToFullyPay() and isMoneyRemaining() are overridden here
